# Workers / Edge Functions — configurar como secrets no Supabase, NUNCA no frontend:
#   supabase secrets set ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=...   (sinal-ia-worker + chatbot; sem ela usa heurística/fallback)
#   supabase secrets set WORKER_SECRET=...       (protege workers e a chamada webhook→chatbot)
#
# Chatbot WhatsApp (Meta Cloud API) — webhook `whatsapp-webhook`:
#   supabase secrets set WHATSAPP_VERIFY_TOKEN=...      (token de verificação do webhook)
#   supabase secrets set WHATSAPP_TOKEN=...             (token permanente da Graph API)
#   supabase secrets set WHATSAPP_PHONE_NUMBER_ID=...   (id do número remetente)
#
# Chatbot Telegram — webhook `telegram-webhook`:
#   supabase secrets set TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=...         (token do bot via @BotFather)
#   supabase secrets set TELEGRAM_WEBHOOK_SECRET=...    (secret_token passado no setWebhook)
